metadata.title: Kids Headphones Wired Over-Ear Foldable LED Gaming Flashing Lights with USB Charger Earphone Headset for iPhone 6s,6s Plus,Android,iPad and Computer (Black&Blue,New Version)
features: [new version]:rechargeable battery by usb cable,adding more lights on both headshade than old version.
[Light Modes]– On/Off Switch Located Behind right "Cat Ear", click it once, LED light long light. Click twice, LED light Twinkle. Click thrice, power off.

[Flexible and Comfortable]:The adjustable height and rotatable ear pads engineered to snuggly put over your ears. Besides, the cushioned ear pads gives you extra comfort when you listen music in a long time.About 20 to 30 hours work time and 4.9ft long cable is much more convenient for you to use it in everywhere.

[Foldable,Adjustable&Removable Headband]: light weight,adjust the headband to fit for any size of head; headband can be removed, you can put on it with newest style headband you love, fashionable and easy to fold & take along

[Universal Compayiility]: Using a standard 3.5mm headphone jack, our cat ear headphones works with virtually all smartphones, tablets, laptops and computers,compatible with iPhone 6S/6S Plus, 6/6 Plus, iPad,iPod, Samsung Galaxy S7, Android Phone, Computer etc
